file.name: missing-parameter-schema.yml
file.content:
---
# An example where some things don't have explicit schemas
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Example
  version: '1.0.1'
paths:
  /test1:
    get:
      parameters:
      - name: param1
        in: query
        description: Missing schema
        required: false
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          headers:
            ResponseHeader:
              description: A response header without a schema

Error: parse: parse spec: parse path items: path "/test1": get: parameters: parse parameter "param1": at 1:105: parameter MUST contain either a schema property, or a content property
